Interface ShealthContract.Constants.HeightUnit

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ShealthSensorDevice.Profile, ShealthSensorDevice.Weight
    Enclosing interface:
    ShealthContract.Constants

    public static interface ShealthContract.Constants.HeightUnit
    This interface defines the height unit types. The user input is in the standard unit of cm. The rest of the defined units are currently for internal use only.
